title: Alan Braxe & Friends - The Upper Cuts
description:
You all remember Stardust - Music Sounds Better With You? Alan Braxe was one of the members of the band, with Benjamin Diamond (house crooner) and Thomas Bangalter (Daft Punk). With more than a touch of the French sound Alan Braxe is one of these artists that produced worldwide hits and his tracks are more famous than his name. For the first time put together on CD , this album gathers most of the hits Alan Braxe produced in their original versions. Different Recordings. 2005.
